description:
With the record of 0-1 on NK, DJ is ready for another chance. He learned a lot from his last match and now he is more focused on scoring points. Martin Lorenzo is a hot New Yorker with a bad attitude. He's new on NK but he acts like he owns the place. It's the battle of two hot ripped studs.
This match was shot before the new scoring format.
title: DJ vs Martin Lorenzo
